This repository is a mixed research package. The license below applies only
to materials that the paper authors or repository maintainers have rights to
license, and it does not relicense excluded or third-party source materials.

## Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International

Author-created repository documentation, package metadata, source-decision
notes, workbook profiles, and rights-cleared aggregate derived table
workbooks and CSV exports are licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution
4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

This includes the curated aggregate paper-table materials under
`data/derived_workbook/` and `data/derived_tables_csv/` only to the extent
they consist of author-created selection, tabulation, analysis, or summaries
controlled by the paper authors or repository maintainers.

## Materials Not Relicensed

This repository license does not apply to:

- The publication PDF under `paper/`, which retains its publication,
  repository, or manuscript terms.
- Raw MnPASS toll-system logs, operator logs, transponder/subscriber records,
  loop-detector density or flow records, price logs, field-experiment records,
  lane operations records, and other MnDOT, MnPASS, public-agency,
  proprietary, or controlled source materials.
- Manuscript-source archives, drafts, review responses, presentations,
  LaTeX/build products, excluded figure or image assets, vendor file-format
  structures, cited references, and other third-party materials.

## Software Boundary

No executable software, scripts, notebooks, model source code, or
paper-specific runtime code are staged in this repository. This root license
therefore grants no separate software license.
